{
  "stem": "15017.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that-- that-- that is the, more or less [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, where we were living in Whitechapel, Stepney, it was a solid Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the school that I went to was Myrtle Street School.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was only one Gentile boy there, whose name was Johnny Abbot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have pictures to prove it, of school pictures that-- that when-- that-- And we went to school until we were 14.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a wonderful headmaster and master by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hadida.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a Sephardic gentleman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whilst I went to school, I was studying music at the Guildhall School of Music.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to go once a week for my lesson.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he used to leave-- the school used to close at 4 o'clock, you know, the day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he used to leave me go at 3:00 so that I could change my clothes and put my best on to take the bus to go to John Carpenter Street, which is in Blackfriars, where the Guildhall School of Music was.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew-- my mother was very, very frum.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Frum, but my father was not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were quite a-- a few amusing anecdotes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I was caught whistling in the house on a Saturday, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, my mother used to give it to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And every Friday, I had to go to shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she used to smell my breath first to find out if I-- all the young boys used to go up, and after the kiddish, everyone took a sip of wine, in Fieldgate Street Shul.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And every week, she used to ask me, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a certain [NON-ENGLISH] there every week, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day-- it's very amusing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
